org.eclipse.emf.facet.efacet.metamodel.v0_2_0.efacet.extensible

Interface Query

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    EObjectLiteralQuery, ETypedElementSwitchQuery, FalseLiteralQuery, FloatLiteralQuery, IntegerLiteralQuery, IsOneOfQuery, JavaQuery, NavigationQuery, NullLiteralQuery, OclQuery, OperationCallQuery, StringLiteralQuery, TrueLiteralQuery, URIImageQuery

    public interface Query
    A representation of the model object 'Query'. Query is the abstract representation of the concept of query. This class has to be sub-classed for each existing query language (Java, OCL, etc.)

    The following features are supported:

    • Can Have Side Effects
    • Can Be Cached

    See Also:
